title.rendered: Adisza Kahanasty debuted its F/W 2022 during Paris Fashion Week

content.rendered:
Fashion Division debuted Indonesian designer Adisza Kahanasty during Paris Fashion Week 2022. The show was held at the prestigious Westin Paris, Vendome 3 rue de Castiglione, 75001 Paris, on the 5th of March 2022 during Paris Fashion Week. The collection embodied craftsmanship and handsome details with timeless and artistry apparel. Storytelling, and recontextualizing the tradition of Indonesian cultures as part of preserving it with a twist of modernized silhouettes for daily wear.

Designer Adisza Kahanasty


By Fashion-editor : Christina V Henningstad  Production: Fashionview
